  div(class="blurb", id="Schāpd-goals")
    div(class="container")
      div(class="row")
        div(class="col-md-12")
          h2 Project Goals
        div(class="col-md-8")
          h4 Goals for Schāpd
          dl
            dt ▴ Show coding proficiency
              dd The ultimate goal for Schāpd is to fulfill the requirements for 
                | the CMSI 402: Senior Project Laboratory course, showcasing all 
                | of the concepts I've learned and all of the knowledge I have aquired
                | during the past four years in LMU's Computer Science program.
            dt ▴ Incorporate Studio Arts minor
              dd Schāpd effectively combines my CS education with my passion for 
                | art and creative expression through building a creativity fueled project.
            dt ▴ Produce a product that empowers others 
              dd In keeping with the university's mission, Schāpd is a project 
                | that hopes to echo the values of educating the whole person and
                | the encouragement of growth. Schāpd was developed in hopes that 
                | it would encourage users to grow their creative energies in a
                | safe, non-judgemental space.  The environment that Schāpd provides 
                | aims to also introduce a non-traditional art style. 
            dt ▴ Challenge myself
              dd In taking on this project, I had no idea what I was getting into.
                | I really wanted to test myself and see if I had the ability to 
                | learn about and implement several tools that I had never used before.
                | (Definitely succeeded on this one.)
        div(class="col-md-4")
