        div(class="col-md-12")
          h2 Schāpd's Challenges
        div(class="col-md-4")
          h4 Time Management
          p Besides the full time student thing, and the senior, Computer Science thing,
            | I partipate in lots of other things...
          img(src='images/clock.png', height='283', width='250')
        div(class="col-md-4")
          h4 Proper Research
          p Half of the work that I did, mainly the developing the shape calculations from first
            | principles took up the majority of my time, and I eventually found a beautiful
            | library with much more elegant solutions than my hacky code.  Unfortunately, I
            | discovered this about two and a half months into the project.
          img(src='images/research.png', height='280', width='280')
        div(class="col-md-4")
          h4 Technology Conflicts
          p Also due to my lack of research, I spent a good amount of time undoing the work
            | that I had previously done.  Many of the technologies I had originally intended 
            | to use did not agree with each other - I had planned to host my app on modulus.io 
            | from the start and later discovered they only provide database support for MongoDB
            | I also toyed with adding a mySQL database as well before returning to PostgreSQL.
          img(src='images/conflict.png', height='280', width='280')

