        div(class="col-md-3")
          h4 Sharing is caring
          p I really hope to, in the near future, implement shape sharing shape information
            | in between friends.  This would encourage even more creative growth and make the
            | app more social.  In the road ahead, I hope to be able to implement a collaborative
            | mode, similar to Google Docs where several people can work on a single canvas at the
            | same time. 
          h4 Tutorials
          p Truly my biggest regret, I really wish that I had time to make tutorials on how to
            | get started thinking with shapes.  Although creation becomes so easy after training,
            | like many other non-traditional practices, getting started is the most difficult step.
